        "text": "Are you familiar with the QOI eco-system? This is the first I'm hearing about it, and I'm immediately suspicious of the airy \"20% better compression\" claim in <https:\/\/github.com\/phoboslab\/qoi#tools|the repo>. Have other people validated this claim, do you know? It feels more believable if they claimed \"20x faster encode\/decode, 20x shorter implementation, 20% worse compression.\"",
